cs.CV, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.LG 

The paper focuses on using deep learning to analyze images and text in social media to infer personality traits. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) as it involves analyzing images, as well as social media analysis (cs.SI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) as it involves analyzing text. Multimedia (cs.MM) is also a likely category as it involves analyzing both images and text. Finally, machine learning (cs.LG) is also a possible category as the paper uses deep neural networks for personality estimation.
